此道通諭的副標題為「照顧我們共同的家園」（On the care for our common home）<ref name="OfficialEngText">{{Cite web | url =http://w2.vatican.va/content/francesco/en/encyclicals/documents/papa-francesco_20150524_enciclica-laudato-si.html | title =Encyclical Letter Laudato Si’ Of The Holy Father Francis On Care For Our Common Home (official English-language text of encyclical) | accessdate =2015-06-18 | archive-date =2016-03-03 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20160303225922/http://w2.vatican.va/content/francesco/en/encyclicals/documents/papa-francesco_20150524_enciclica-laudato-si.html | dead-url =no }}</ref>，主題為[[生态|生态]]問題。在通諭中，他批判了[[消費主義|消費主義]]和{{link-en|過度發展|Overdevelopment}}。方濟各呼籲各方進行積極對話，共同採取迅速且一致的行動，以對抗[[環境退化|環境退化]]與氣候變化（即[[全球暖化|全球暖化]]），他期待有關方面做出恰當決策<ref name=radiovaticana.va /><ref name="NYT">{{cite news | first1 = Jim | last1 = Yardley | first2 = Laurie | last2 = Goodstein | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2015/06/19/world/europe/pope-francis-in-sweeping-encyclical-calls-for-swift-action-on-climate-change.html | title = Pope Francis, in Sweeping Encyclical, Calls for Swift Action on Climate Change | work = The New York Times | date = 2015-06-18 | accessdate = 2015-06-20 | archive-date = 2015-06-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150620235551/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/06/19/world/europe/pope-francis-in-sweeping-encyclical-calls-for-swift-action-on-climate-change.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

此道通諭以[[意大利语|意大利语]]、[[法语|法语]]、[[英语|英语]]、[[德语|德语]]、[[西班牙语|西班牙语]]、[[葡萄牙语|葡萄牙语]]同时发表<ref name=2015-06-10 />，上一道通諭是《{{link-en|信德之光|Lumen fidei}}》，於2013年7月發表<ref name=2013-07-05>{{cite web|title=«信德之光»通谕简介|url=http://zh.radiovaticana.va/storico/2013/07/05/%C2%AB%E4%BF%A1%E5%BE%B7%E4%B9%8B%E5%85%89%C2%BB%E9%80%9A%E8%B0%95%E7%AE%80%E4%BB%8B/ci2-707935|publisher=梵蒂冈广播电台|accessdate=2015-06-19|date=2013-07-05|archive-date=2015-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150620065401/http://zh.radiovaticana.va/storico/2013/07/05/%C2%AB%E4%BF%A1%E5%BE%B7%E4%B9%8B%E5%85%89%C2%BB%E9%80%9A%E8%B0%95%E7%AE%80%E4%BB%8B/ci2-707935|dead-url=no}}</ref>；因為《信德之光》主要由[[教宗本篤十六世|教宗本篤十六世]]（方濟各的前任）撰寫，所以《愿祢受赞颂》是第一道完全由方濟各撰寫的通諭<ref name="Crux">{{cite news | first = Inés | last = San Martín | url = http://www.cruxnow.com/church/2015/06/17/laudato-si-will-be-an-encyclical-for-the-ages/ | title = 'Laudato Si' will be an encyclical for the ages | date = 2015-06-17 | publisher = Crux | access-date = 2015-06-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150618211209/http://www.cruxnow.com/church/2015/06/17/laudato-si-will-be-an-encyclical-for-the-ages/ | archive-date = 2015-06-18 | dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref name=things>{{cite news | first1 = Francis X. | last1 = Rocca | first2 = Stephen | last2 = Nakrosis | url = http://blogs.wsj.com/briefly/2015/06/18/5-things-to-know-about-pope-francis-encyclical-laudato-si/ | title = 5 Things to Know About Pope Francis' Encyclical 'Laudato Si' | work = Wall Street Journal | date = 2015-06-18 | accessdate = 2015-06-20 | archive-date = 2015-06-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150620232739/http://blogs.wsj.com/briefly/2015/06/18/5-things-to-know-about-pope-francis-encyclical-laudato-si/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 簡介 ==
通諭，是指[[天主教|天主教]]的教宗，對全世界[[天主教徒|天主教徒]]所下達的教導信件，內容為宣揚教義與[[道德|道德]]。通常作長篇，主文為[[拉丁文|拉丁文]]，在發布的同時，也會有其他重要語言的譯文。文章開頭的兩個拉丁字，為通諭的正式名稱<ref>{{cite web|author1=孫靜潛|title=通諭 Encyclical|url=http://terms.naer.edu.tw/detail/1310844/?index=1|publisher=[[國家教育研究院|國家教育研究院]]|accessdate=2015-06-20|date=2000年12月|archive-date=2015-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150621032138/http://terms.naer.edu.tw/detail/1310844/?index=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在以往歷史，通諭只對宗教議題發表立場；不過近來的各任教宗，也已不再侷限於宗教方面；由於全世界的天主教徒約有12億人，所以教宗通諭的影響力相當大<ref name=TVBS-N>{{cite news|title=教宗通諭警告氣候變遷　右派批撈過界|url=https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%95%99%E5%AE%97%E9%80%9A%E8%AB%AD%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E6%B0%A3%E5%80%99%E8%AE%8A%E9%81%B7-%E5%8F%B3%E6%B4%BE%E6%89%B9%E6%92%88%E9%81%8E%E7%95%8C-151800897.html|accessdate=2015-06-20|agency=[[TVBS-N|TVBS-N]]|date=2015-06-18|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150621023852/https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%95%99%E5%AE%97%E9%80%9A%E8%AB%AD%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E6%B0%A3%E5%80%99%E8%AE%8A%E9%81%B7-%E5%8F%B3%E6%B4%BE%E6%89%B9%E6%92%88%E9%81%8E%E7%95%8C-151800897.html|archivedate=2015-06-21}}</ref><ref name=Yuan>{{cite news|author1=Yuan|title=教宗方濟各通諭：地球已在對我們的作為表示抗議|url=http://www.thenewslens.com/post/177191/|accessdate=2015-06-20|agency=[[關鍵評論網|關鍵評論網]]|date=2015-06-16|archive-date=2015-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150621010153/http://www.thenewslens.com/post/177191/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

通諭的原文標題「Laudato si'」是{{link-en|義大利中部方言|Central Italian|翁布里亚}}語<ref name="Crux"/>，引自[[十三世紀|十三世紀]]的天主教聖人[[亞西西的方濟各|亞西西的方濟各]]所作的《太陽頌歌》（{{lang|en|Canticle of the Sun}}），亦稱《萬物頌歌》（Canticle of the Creatures）。這篇作品是一首詩歌，讚美上主創造了[[地球|地球]]的一切萬物與生命<ref name=bulletin>{{cite web | url = https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2015/06/10/0451/00975.html | title = Avviso di Conferenza Stampa, 10.06.2015 | publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |date =2015-06-10 |language=it |accessdate=2019-07-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190715065443/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2015/06/10/0451/00975.html |archivedate=2019-07-15}}</ref>。根據《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》的[[摘要|摘要]]，此道通諭涉及的範圍是全面的<ref name="NYT"/>。方濟各描述了一個受到持續不斷[[自然資源的開採|剝削]]和[[环境退化|破壞]]的環境，為此他指責為了追求獲利的冷漠和不顾后果、於[[政治|政治]]上的短視，以及對[[科技|科技]]的過度信賴<ref name="NYT"/>。文中明確接受「氣候變化很大程度是源自人為」的[[關於氣候變化的科學意見|科學家意見]]<ref name=eco>{{cite news | url = http://www.cruxnow.com/church/2015/06/19/popes-environmental-manifesto-looks-like-a-game-changer-in-the-us/ | 2 =  | last = Allen, Jr. | first = John L. | work = Crux | authorlink = John L. Allen, Jr. | date = 2015-06-19 | accessdate = 2015-06-19 | title = Pope’s eco-manifesto looks like a game-changer in the U | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150619202311/http://www.cruxnow.com/church/2015/06/19/popes-environmental-manifesto-looks-like-a-game-changer-in-the-us/ | archive-date = 2015-06-19 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>，並指「氣候變化是全球問題，其嚴重影響了包括環境、社会、經濟、政治，與物品分配，它代表着今日吾人所面臨的重大挑戰之一。」；他更警告假如再不迅速為了{{link-en|減緩氣候變化|Climate change mitigation}}着手努力，則「史无前例的[[生态系统|生态系统]]破坏，將對我们所有人造成嚴重後果」<ref name="NYT"/><ref name="OfficialEngText"/>。

文中的另一個重點是，[[化石燃料|化石燃料]]在造成氣候變化中的角色，與[[已開發國家|已開發國家]]在道义上，有义务帮助[[发展中国家|发展中国家]]對抗氣候變化危機<ref name="NYT"/>。教宗說，貧窮國還沒準備好{{link-en|適應全球暖化|Adaptation to global warming}}，且將承擔[[全球变暖的效应|全球变暖的效应]]的衝擊<ref name=eco/>。與此關聯的問題是[[貧窮|貧窮]]，這也是他在教宗期間的主要關注問題之一；他強調，全世界必須「聽見地球和窮人的哭喊」<ref name=eco/>。

通諭有172條[[腳註|腳註]]<ref name="OfficialEngText"/>，很多部份參自[[教宗若望保祿二世|教宗若望保祿二世]]和[[教宗本篤十六世|教宗本篤十六世]]<ref name="NYT"/>；另外，他也引用了來自他的盟友，[[正教會|正教會]][[君士坦丁堡普世牧首|君士坦丁堡普世牧首]][[巴爾多祿茂一世|巴爾多祿茂一世]]<ref name="NYT"/>，以及前人如聖人[[托马斯·阿奎那|托马斯·阿奎那]]，9世紀的[[蘇非主義|蘇非主義]]者{{tsl|en|Ali al-Khawas|Ali al-Khawas}}<ref name="NYT"/><ref name=mystic>{{cite news|author1=Aisha Bhoori|title=Meet the Muslim Mystic Pope Francis Cited in His Encyclical|url=http://time.com/3927357/pope-francis-ali-al-khawas/|accessdate=2015-06-19|work=TIME|archive-date=2015-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150618212113/http://time.com/3927357/pope-francis-ali-al-khawas/|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[德日进|德日进]]、{{link-en|郭蒂尼|Romano Guardini}}等人的言論<ref name=Faggioli>{{cite news |first=Massimo |last=Faggioli |url=https://www.commonwealmagazine.org/global-warning |title=Global Warning: Pope Francis's Environmental Encyclical |work=[[Commonweal|Commonweal]] |date=2015-06-18 |accessdate=2015-06-18 |archive-date=2015-06-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150618211234/https://www.commonwealmagazine.org/global-warning |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

